    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哈娜花园里的音乐花朵散落在天空各处的美丽小岛中，她必须求助神奇的弹波波，帮她将这些花朵找回来。弹波波生性调皮又笨拙，它们要依靠哈娜的指挥才能跟上节奏，解开各个小岛的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/318840/extras/6e8fa2412552df308a3d0880b83ab598.poster.avif?t=1760522789\" width=610 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/318840/extras/6e8fa2412552df308a3d0880b83ab598.webm?t=1760522789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/318840/extras/6e8fa2412552df308a3d0880b83ab598.mp4?t=1760522789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四季谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座小岛都将考验你的规划与执行能力。尝试不同的配置和路线，让每只弹波波各司其职，互相撞击、堆叠、抬起和推动，共同解开春夏秋冬的不同谜题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >乐声悠扬</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个明亮欢乐的世界充满了音乐，所有生物都随着同一个跳动声起舞。配乐由荣获英国电影学院奖的作曲家兼音频总监Jeff van Dyck制作，每一个音符都让人陶醉。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成长空间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每解开一个谜题，你拯救的花朵都会加入你的旋律花园。每种花朵都会吟唱自己的旋律，你可以将它们排列组合，享受独特的音乐表演。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/318840/extras/ce1022f9ffc0d90b34f22e349b6203b1.poster.avif?t=1760522789\" width=610 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/318840/extras/ce1022f9ffc0d90b34f22e349b6203b1.webm?t=1760522789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/318840/extras/ce1022f9ffc0d90b34f22e349b6203b1.mp4?t=1760522789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
